## Write a program to check upper case

Check if the given character is upper case (A-Z).

```
Input  : A
Output : Upper Case
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="check-upper-case" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main(){

    char ch;
    scanf("%c",&ch);
    if(ch>='A' && ch<='Z') printf("Upper Case");
    else printf("Not Upper Case");
    return 0;
}
```

